WEBVTT

00:08:29.729 --> 00:08:31.929
lakini mpelelezi huyu
alifanya kitu tofauti.

00:08:31.953 --> 00:08:34.540
Aliangalia ambacho hakipo,
ambapo ni ngumu kufanya.

00:08:35.045 --> 00:08:36.360
Na aliuliza swali:

00:08:36.384 --> 00:08:39.296
kama kweli mashua ilipinduka --

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:41.538
kama mashuhuda wanavyosema --

00:08:41.562 --> 00:08:44.317
inakuwaje makaratasi yaliyowekwa
mwisho mmoja wa mashua

00:08:44.341 --> 00:08:45.942
yapo makavu kabisa?

00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:50.288
Kulingana na mtazamo huo
mdogo lakini muhimu,

00:08:50.312 --> 00:08:54.273
upelelezi ulihama kutoka
katika kifo mpaka mauaji.

00:08:56.257 --> 00:08:58.897
Sasa, muhimu kusema kipi
kisichokuwepo pale

00:08:58.921 --> 00:09:03.540
ni uwezo wa kutafuta muunganiko wa
uono ambapo vitu havionekani.